==========<<INSTRUCTIONS>>=============

IN BATTLE, use the ARROWKEYS/WASD to choose an action and confirm with SPACEBAR.

I decided to do something I haven't seen in a generic platformer before... Instead of just one boring ending, there's >>ELEVEN ENDINGS<<! Which one you get depends on your choices... Can you find them all??

(I am not trying to target anyone btw)

description:

This boss is the hardest one yet!

Sorry for the wait, enjoy! :)
instructions:
- STICKMAN HERO'S QUEST PART 5 -

> Press Z to progress talking and reading.

- BASIC CONTROLS -
> Arrow keys or WASD to move, up or W to jump
> Hold down or S to crouch
> Move while crouching to crouch walk
> Jump while crouching to crouch jump
>Touch vines to grab them, then jump at the bottom of the swing for the best dismount!

- IN BATTLE MODE -

Stickman:
> Space or mouse tap to attack
> Attack while idle - PUNCH
> Attack + run - SLIDE KICK
> Attack + down key - KICK
> 1-2 keys to use specials
> Attack + midair + forward directional key - DIVE

Hunter Girl:
> Attack while idle - SPEAR STAB
> Attack + run - SPEAR THROW (aim with mouse)
> Attack + down key - LONG STAB
> 1-2 keys to use specials

- GOAL -
Explore the forest in search for the thieves' base!
